---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About ATECH | Energy Audit & Sustainability Consultancy Malaysia"
  description="Meet the team behind ATECH Sustainability Consultancy — MAESCO Gold Award winners delivering expert energy audits, training, and sustainability solutions across Malaysia."
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About ATECH</h1>
      <p>MAESCO Gold Award-winning sustainability consultancy serving Malaysian businesses.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        ATECH Sustainability Consultancy (ASC) is a Malaysian energy and sustainability
        consultancy dedicated to helping organisations reduce energy costs, lower carbon
        emissions, and achieve long-term environmental goals.
      </p>
      <p>
        We were awarded the <strong>MAESCO Gold Award for Energy Management Excellence 2025</strong>
        by the Malaysian Association of Energy Service Companies, in recognition of our
        proven capability in delivering measurable energy performance solutions.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our work spans energy audits, HRDC-claimable training, Registered Energy Manager
        (REM) mentorship, and green financing advisory. We serve clients nationwide,
        from Klang Valley to Penang, Johor, Sabah, and Sarawak.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Approach</h2>
      <p>
        We believe that <em>"if you can't measure it, you can't manage it."</em> Every
        engagement begins with rigorous data collection and on-site assessment, followed
        by clear, actionable recommendations backed by financial analysis.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our audits are fully compliant with government energy audit standards and the
        Energy Efficiency and Conservation Act (EECA) 2023. We
        use AI-assisted tooling to deliver faster, more consistent reviews, while
        keeping expert human judgment at the centre of every recommendation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h2>Ready to Work Together?</h2>
      <p style="max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 2rem;">
        Whether you need an energy audit, training programme, or sustainability advisory,
        we'd love to help.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
